光在回复用户询问时给出可能有害的回答。7月，记者发现，“Gemini”就各种健康问题给出了错误的、可能致命的信息，例如它建议人们“每天至少吃一块小石子”以补充维生素和矿物质。谷歌当时回应称，它已经对“Gemini”就健康问题回复时包含的讽刺和幽默网站信息进行了限制。 （参考来源：https://weibo.com/1686546714/5102366057565612）"},"attached_info":"CkEI3svVweLL/a4NEAMaCTExMTg5MTM3NyCWgPG5BjAAONIGQBtyCjQ1NzMzMjE3NDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2dc54bf0a32e420bae5e3689fb4b5240_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1732419403.310818","card_id":"Q_273445842","target":{"id":273445842,"title":"如何评价小浣熊水浒卡的艺术价值？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/273445842","type":"question","created":1523851338,"answer_count":197,"follower_count":2190,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2040,3352,4364,113549,156313],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"小浣熊水浒卡是很多人童年回忆的一部分，但是抛开情怀加成来看，小浣熊水浒卡究竟有多少艺术价值呢？ 个人认为，角色立绘的设计大多都很有创意，绘图也很精美，蕴含了大量的传统文化元素且忠于水浒原著。卡背面的文案也很精彩，技能名什么的大多也都挺帅气的。数据也很科学，至少我这样一个读过水浒原著很多遍的人是挑不出很大的毛病。 不知道万能的知友们怎么看？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3svVweLL/a4NEAMaCDIzMDQwOTEyIMrA0NYFMAA4jhFAHHIJMjczNDQ1ODQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d095697237489c69d3cad1cb7ddf512_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1732419403.313162","card_id":"Q_4612080123","target":{"id":4612080123,"title":"如何评价悬疑剧《白夜追凶》第二部 《白夜破晓》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4612080123","type":"question","created":1732036748,"answer_count":236,"follower_count":463,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,185085,213156,378953],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"《白夜追凶》七